        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks GM for his fair review [of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Zoologist</hi> 19 (1861): 7577–611].</p> 
            <p>Feels it is a pity to mingle science and religion;</p>
            <p>explains why he did not deal with the case of man.</p>
        </abstract>
